ᴢᴀɴᴅᴠᴏᴏʀᴛ, ʏᴏᴜ ᴀʀᴇ sᴏᴍᴇᴛʜɪɴɢ ᴇʟsᴇ 🧡

To see such a sea of Orange out there on a Friday was 💯

The crowd and track made it very enjoyable to be out there although it was a bit of a stop and start day 

I couldn’t really get a good short run in, so we’ll have some work to do before Quali tomorrow

I really enjoyed myself out there, thank you to everyone involved for the amazing atmosphere 🇳🇱

See you all tomorrow!

🤩🤩🤩

Such an amazing feeling to drive out and see this today 🧡

Unbelievable to have so many fans here on a Friday already🙏🏻 🇳🇱

#SuperFriday #DutchGP

node.text:
🔴⚪️🔵

A home GP calls for a special design 🇳🇱

Hope you guys love it as much as I do!

For all mini helmets 👉 link in bio

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Max Verstappen in Circuit de Spa-Francorchamps with @redbullracing, and @hondaracingf1. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
Let me start of with thanking the fans. I feel so so sorry for all of you that came out today but thank you so much for the amazing support over the weekend 🙏🏻 🧡

At the end of the day we will take the result and I am very happy we could give @hondaracingf1 a win for their 50th race with the team

Now we move on to Zandvoort

node.text: R A C E D A Y 🦁🇧🇪🔸

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Max Verstappen on August 28, 2021. May be an image of one or more people.

node.text:
sɪᴍᴘʟʏ ʟᴏᴠᴇʟʏ 

This is a very special track to drive for me but so challenging in the wet 😅

The conditions made it a tricky Quali and I am very happy we managed P1 after another great effort by @redbullracing and @hondaracingf1💪

Thanks to the Orange Army for the support out there, hope you all enjoyed it as much as I did! 🧡
